title: Multiple injuries reported in crash at Oklahoma State parade
text:
Multiple injuries reported in crash at Oklahoma State University homecoming parade THE ASSOCIATED PRESS   12:55 pmLast   12:55 pm   
Subjects: 
Oklahoma (553) 

STILLWATER, Oklahoma â€” Authorities are reporting injuries after a vehicle crashed into spectators during the Oklahoma State University homecoming parade in Stillwater. 
Oklahoma Highway Patrol Lt. John Vincent said there are multiple injuries as a result of the Saturday morning incident, but that he had no further details. 
Phone calls to Stillwater police and to Oklahoma State officials were not immediately returned. 
Oklahoma State is to host Kansas in its annual homecoming game Saturday afternoon.
